{"tid":447123,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"速成撚轉倉頡","createTime":"2017-10-25T03:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T02:59:52.000Z","uid":40493,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"612cc501496cafd786343c07196fb117f565d9a8","tid":447123,"uid":40493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:47:12.000Z","msg":"想問巴打有無Software 或者書推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：打左十幾年速成，唔知轉唔轉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9ce788a807c229b62aae927235587d2a2afa4e","tid":447123,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"求其一本<br />\n每日坐定定練一個鐘"},{"pid":"6fd46a63efb4c6bdd7806dd89c4c0cf3c0f73562","tid":447123,"uid":40792,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"洗咩software架<br />\n我都打左好耐速成轉倉頡<br />\n係咁以上網睇下佢取碼既方法就學到<br />\n用左倉頡返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a457df9310bbd9e1263cd49d1ed6c863e1595a","tid":447123,"uid":36478,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"結果變咗<br />\n頭碼＊尾碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637c628eab391f3613e54e838726db52b8a82bc2","tid":447123,"uid":48776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問巴打有無Software 或者書推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：打左十幾年速成，唔知轉唔轉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗睇書架...<br />\n我打左至少8年速成<br />\n自學轉左倉頡 一個星期就已經上左手(日日打機)<br />\n<br />\nwindows內置可以set到 打[頭碼＊尾碼] (姐係速成咁)<br />\n簡完隻字會顯示埋成隻字既倉頡碼出黎"},{"pid":"e88616325de551bfdbdf525cb0081d271e595e20","tid":447123,"uid":40493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"我怕5分鐘就裝番速成黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fbffa5cbd2bec725b36c35e8d453488e19e8c5","tid":447123,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結果變咗<br />\n頭碼＊尾碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b085be009f46803c55cf8b1f5fcbb5c18f6e40da","tid":447123,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"點解要轉"},{"pid":"0a2f4ed0da3b4fead91a9bc4a34bcab2d6958071","tid":447123,"uid":42338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"去公共圖書館是但借一本教倉頡嘅書<br />\n正路應該一個chapter教一款拆字規則 chapter尾有啲練習咁<br />\n每日練一兩個chapter 打晒一本你覺得夠就開始唔用"},{"pid":"27dce2209b771e34964f559e16944dd838abc8f0","tid":447123,"uid":42338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去公共圖書館是但借一本教倉頡嘅書<br />\n正路應該一個chapter教一款拆字規則 chapter尾有啲練習咁<br />\n每日練一兩個chapter 打晒一本你覺得夠就開始唔用</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6289dceb57999d5ddf5349c76928ab2b5a52d81b","tid":447123,"uid":124983,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"轉黎托<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b95b62aef17afca22c804067c3ab65fc296ded3","tid":447123,"uid":146172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇書 對住個表打幾日就會識 唔識就上網查碼 試多幾次就得"},{"pid":"d48e12720e6f32bb6ebcac40faf26aa1ce25487d","tid":447123,"uid":15823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>結果變咗<br />\n頭碼＊尾碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無痛轉換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b6629307b5cf85b688599a335b15697fb396e5","tid":447123,"uid":31837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:40:22.000Z","msg":"其實識速成，倉頡真係唔難學，因為啲複雜嘅字，個rule都係拎首碼+尾碼再搭少少變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c9f8a3d6af976e5d45d35cabd755da325bf319","tid":447123,"uid":27719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:44:13.000Z","msg":"爸打係咪我，我啱啱都轉緊<br />\n一有唔識就查<br />\n不過係手機用多<br />\n電腦就未轉到"},{"pid":"a2d7a4a30512ce06c253d35eafaee7ff2ee72da4","tid":447123,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"轉左<br />\n動機係之前用垃圾window phone未有速成<br />\n結論 勇敢d remove速成 得返倉頡 <br />\n唔識打主動上網search就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2c1240e3420481ded55e86d2547d6e8b5ba64d","tid":447123,"uid":40493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"已刪速成, 希望唔會忍唔住裝番<br />\n<br />\n呢幾隻字打左我差唔多15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e196daf033082767481d23c5e08eaa79d702430c","tid":447123,"uid":59922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"係要記住啲特別字嘅拆法啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0541201b397288228e24a9c4477b17dccb0bae21","tid":447123,"uid":40493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係要記住啲特別字嘅拆法啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都要記熟番個字碼表, 以前打速成大部份都